item.description:
Weather is going to be very nice so Plunk and I are going for a romp in Benedictine park after work on Tuesday. Rumor has it that one of our peeps (Carolyn) is also celebrating a birthday this week.

So hopefully Carolyn and Kay will show up so we can sing "arf arf arf" for her birthday.
item.how_to_find_us: Plunk will be running around in circles, doing pig snorts and screaming Here I am......catch me if you can !!!
